Key Match Events: Deniz Undav scored twice for Germany in the first half
Edin Dzeko scored a goal for Bosnia-Herzegovina in the second half
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was played at the Bilino Polje Stadium in Zenica, Bosnia and Herzegovina
Others: Germany moved to seven points from three games in League A Group 3
Bosnia-Herzegovina dropped to fourth after equaling their longest-ever winless run of nine straight matches
